      <longTitle>
        <p>Amendment to the <ref href="/akn/poc/bill/paella-reform-2024">Paella Reform Bill</ref>: <docTitle>Protected Designation of Origin</docTitle></p>
      </longTitle>
      <p>Submitted by <docProponent>Representative Valencia</docProponent>.</p>
    </preface>

    <amendmentBody>
      <amendmentContent>
        <block name="amendment">
          <p>It is proposed to add a new <ref href="/akn/poc/act/valencian-paella-recipe#art_11">Article 12</ref> on protected designation:</p>
          <p><ins>"Article 12. Protected designation. Only a preparation that fully complies with this Act may be called 'Valencian Paella'. Any variation must use a different name."</ins></p>
        </block>
        <block name="justification">
          <p>It is essential to protect the designation 'Valencian Paella' as intangible cultural heritage. Allowing variations without a name change dilutes our gastronomic identity.</p>
        </block>
      </amendmentContent>
    </amendmentBody>
